caption.p: Projected changes in probabilities of occurrence of (a) Lesser Yellowlegs and (b) Baird's Sandpiper based on two general circulation models, the warmer wetter IPSL‐ CM5B‐ LR, Representative Concentration Pathway 8.5 (top panels), and the hotter drier ACCESS1‐0, Representative Concentration Pathway 8.5 (bottom panels). Minimum and maximum values across the study area are provided in parentheses
